"v.反驳，驳斥 【英】 v. 反驳,驳斥(affirm the contrary of a statement, etc) 【记】 contra(反)+dict(说 话,断言)→反说→反驳 【同】 派生词: contradiction (n.反驳, 矛盾); contradictory (adj.互相矛盾的) v. (表达对一种说法的反对)反驳 = deny 【记】contra反, dict说－反着你的意思说－反驳 【参】contradiction(n 反驳; 矛盾); contrary(n 反面; adj /adv 相反)contradictory(adj 反驳的; n 矛盾因素; 对立物); 【类】paradox: contradictory = epigram: wise自相矛盾的话是矛盾的 = 警句是明智的oxymoron: contradictory = mishap: catastrophic矛盾修饰法是矛盾的 = 不幸是灾难的 【记】contra contary反 + dict 说 【相关】contradict 驳斥， dictate 口述，edict 法令，indict 控告，maledict 诅咒，predict预言，valedict告别，verdict定论 contradict (v.)  1570s, ""speak against,"" also ""assert the contrary"" (1580s), from Latin contradictus, past participle of contradicere (see contradiction). Related: Contradicted; contradicting; contradictive."
